summary: An abandoned farmhouse located outside Riverwood.
descriptionHtml:
An abandoned farmhouse located outside Riverwood. This allows the player to have a basic home at the start of the game without having to purchase one. Comes with a bookshelf, chest and some other basic features. Perfect for a starter home in Skyrim.

"coc riverwoodhome" - Access from Console
author: John Jamesonsonson
